milestones.description: Hadlee has become the top wicket-taker for NZ in ODIs with 26 wickets, going past Lance Cairns's 23
John Parker has broken the record for most catches in an innings (3) in ODIs for NZ, going past John Parker's 2
Chatfield and Warren Lees's 21-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 17 between Howarth and Hadlee
Mark Burgess has broken the record for most ODIs (8) as captain for NZ, going past Bevan Congdon
